{
  "text": "\u03ea/\u03ea mice and wildtype mice produced similar amounts of B. hermsii-specific IgM as determined by ELISA. This finding is consistent with previous findings of normal or even elevated IgM production in MyD88 \u03ea/\u03ea mice infected with B. burgdorferi [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
